 103x \equiv 444 \pmod{ 999}
11T\equiv 17\pmod{24}
11^2\equiv 1\pmod{24}
11
103x=444+999a
a
103x=111(4+9a)
\frac{103x}{111}=4+9a
\implies 111\mid x
x=111y\implies 103y=4+9a
\implies 103y\equiv4\pmod 9
\implies 4y\equiv4\pmod 9
\implies y\equiv1\pmod 9
(4,9)=1,y=9b+1
b
x=111y=111(9b+1)\equiv 111\pmod{999}
